was the own Chancellor Democrat , Werner Faymann , who announced this decision after a Council of Ministers , when the debt public Austrian high the 74,6 % , a figure very higher the limit maximum the 60 % at by the Treaty of Maastricht , but clearly from to the debts of countries as Italy , Greece or Spain .
